$iterator->toList(); // Returns [[1, 3], [2, 4]]
```

You can also chose a custom function to zip the elements together, such
as doing a sum by index:

### Example

```
$iterator = new ZipIterator([[1, 2], [3, 4]], function ($a, $b) {
return $a + $b;
});
$iterator->toList(); // Returns [4, 6]
```

